:JOURNEY
Rereading Between the World and Me
Read
Impact
- First read | 5 | Urgent and precise | Unlike anything I had encountered in this form
- Second read | 5 | Letter structure lands | Clearer and more devastating on reread
- Third read | 4 | History gains weight | Deepened by broader historical reading
- Recent reads | 5 | Fear lands differently | His fear for his son changes every year

